beer.beer_description: I have memories of drinking pints of Double Dragon from the Felinfoel brewery out of a keg on the back of a pickup in Twickenham car park. This lightly hopped, malty beer is aiming to reproduce some of the style of the beer brewed in the valleys of South Wales. We sourced Bramling and Whitbread hops to ensure we were hitting the right flavours for this beer.
